o teach special versions of calculus courses for their most mathematically advanced entering first-year students, as might its older sibling text Multivariable and Vector Calculus which appeared in 2020 and is intended for students who take and do well on the AP BC exam.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 06. Mrz 2024) 0aCalculus. 0aSequences (Mathematics) 0aSequences (Mathematics). 4aFolgen und Reihen. 4aInfinitesimalrechnung. 4aReelle Zahlen. 4aUnbestimmte Integrale. 7aMATHEMATICS / Mathematical Analysis.2bisacsh  aIndefinite Integrals.  aInfinitesimal Calculus.  aReal Numbers.  aSequences and Series.1 aFehribach, Joseph D., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2023 Part 1z978311117578208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishz978311131929208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023z9783111318912oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Mathematics 2023 Englishz978311131920908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Mathematics 2023z9783111318608oZDB-23-DMA0 cEPUBz97831107684660 cprintz978311076835040uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311076839840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110768398423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110768398/original  a978-3-11-117578-2  DG Plus DeG Package 2023 Part 1b2023  a978-3-11-131920-9  EBOOK PACKAGE Mathematics 2023 Englishb2023  a978-3-11-131929-2  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2023 Englishb2023  aEBA_CL_MTPY  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_MTPY  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESTMALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-DGGb2023  aZDB-23-DMAb2023